OL,3,C'It's so depressing': Struggling local
OL,4,Ccouncils scrap Christmas cheer as
OL,5,Cbankruptcy looms
OL,7,FLocal councils across the country have
OL,8,Fopted to cancel Christmas markets and
OL,9,Fother festivities this year as an
OL,10,Fincreasing number of them face
OL,11,Fbankruptcy.
OL,13,FAlmost one in five council leaders in
OL,14,FEngland say they expect to declare
OL,15,Fbankruptcy either this year or next.
OL,17,FBoth Nottingham and Birmingham
OL,18,Fcouncils have filed section 114
OL,19,Fnotices this year, which is the
OL,20,Fequivalent process to a business
OL,21,Fdeclaring bankruptcy.
